{"tid":1846573,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人開始諗自己奶左肺炎會點做？","createTime":"2020-01-27T16:16:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-01T22:01:44.000Z","uid":189404,"like":52,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"80337e010cd5eabb86ea0df523f295a5227e40c7","tid":1846573,"uid":189404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T16:16:02.000Z","msg":"1.預左有機會死，已經寫定所有戶口號碼加密碼，擺床下底。<br />\n<br />\n2.撚到狗就會去狗屋撚狗，本人好鐘意狗，若果有機會死當然係撚盡佢。<br />\n<br />\n3.橫掂無藥醫，屋企環境點都好過醫院，買定兩箱寶礦力，兩箱加營素放床下底，床頭擺熱水機。有疑似奶野就一番屋企就自閉，嚴重就刪埋房門開暖風焗桑拿，自己開奶飲or飲寶礦力，直到好番或者死。<br />\n<br />\n4.住村屋，屋企人可以住樓上，獨立樓梯零接觸。"},{"pid":"2bcd76ee394f7fa55eb165ef649c48c8119f7657","tid":1846573,"uid":189404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T16:17:19.000Z","msg":"有冇人想分享？"},{"pid":"89aeadf9b14a9b24a5c4648477a828465bfea382","tid":1846573,"uid":189404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T16:21:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"567cd55454fdf59d2639b1108bb291c1b9531e85","tid":1846573,"uid":144522,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T16:21:52.000Z","msg":"最怕到臨死嗰刻都未知中招就訓低咗"},{"pid":"4d1b28c55fdacd4ae98b88fa373dd039f879e67f","tid":1846573,"uid":189404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"567cd55454fdf59d2639b1108bb291c1b9531e85","tid":1846573,"uid":144522,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T16:21:52.000Z","msg":"最怕到臨死嗰刻都未知中招就訓低咗"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T16:22:34.000Z","msg":"應該唔會掛，係都無計"},{"pid":"0dbbc6f1642c59304d8d609d4263a4e0fd262961","tid":1846573,"uid":224545,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T16:23:00.000Z","msg":"馬會"},{"pid":"158875df6fc11aabb4577535d6d8a48d79305176","tid":1846573,"uid":189404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0dbbc6f1642c59304d8d609d4263a4e0fd262961","tid":1846573,"uid":224545,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T16